        <text><![CDATA[ <p><strong>Renewable HVAC Energy And Technology for Schools Act or the Renewable HEAT for Schools Act</strong></p> <p>This bill requires the Department of Energy to make grants to local educational agencies for encouraging schools to use heating and cooling systems that use renewable energy.</p>]]></text>
